Itel Mobile’s new and existing customers are in for a treat this season as the firm is giving thousands of customers across a chance to win 10,000 dollars in the new season of winnings promo. This mega-promo is touted to be itel’s biggest ever. The promo runs till June 30. The promo is the brand’s way of appreciating its customers for their unwavering loyalty and affinity over the years. To be among the lucky winners, all you need do is buy any of itel’s latest power devices, itel P33 or P33 Plus at any itel authorised retail stores nationwide, register your details at this link bit.ly/itel10k, and you could be one of several people to win $10,000, $2,000, or $1,000.